*"10014363 V1.1" (or something like that) is silkscreened :on the board in the FCC photos (under ''Luxul'''s filing). The board looks pretty much identical to the W1800R's board.
This router looks highly similar, if not identical to, the [[Tenda W1800R]]. *The dimensions and power requirements also match up exactly.. :so this device is assumed to be a rebranded W1800R. The FCC ID of the W1800R has also been assigned to this entry.
Additional specifications, per '''Luxul''''s datasheet, follow... *Dimensions (L x W x H): [[Dimensions::218.6 mm x 156.5 mm x 33.8 mm]]
